Azumi Says He Will Tell G-7 Japan Ready to Take ‘Bold’ Action on Currency

-- B y   T o r u   F u j i o k a
-- 
2011-09-08T22:09:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/azumi-says-he-will-tell-g-7-japan-ready-to-take-bold-action-on-currency.html
Japanese Finance Minister Jun Azumi
said he will tell his Group of Seven counterparts that his
country remains prepared to take “bold” action in currency
markets when necessary. He spoke to reporters today in
Marseille,  France .  To contact the reporter on this story:
